title: OUC Viewing Party Competition Results!
body:
Congratulations to RMIT University for having the most votes! They will be getting Razer support for their viewing party on the 30th of August for the OUC Grand Finals. I will be in touch with [RMIT LoG](https://www.facebook.com/groups/RMITLoLClub/) to organise the event.

Voting was pretty close, below you can see the top 3.

1. **RMIT University** - 217
2. University of Wollongong - 183
3. Queensland University of Technology - 130

Don't worry though, all universities that host a viewing party for the OUC Grand Finals will be receiving League of Legends goodies to give away regardless.
